721531f-b.title: Manhattan: Madison Street - Oliver Street
721531f-b.text:
(1)
Madison Street, north side, east from but not including Oliver
Street. The view shows the Downtown Tammany Club, on the right,
at No. 59-61 Madison Street, north side, between Oliver and Catherine
Streets. The building adjoining same (No. 63) is a 3-story frame
house with a brick front.
October 8, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPPODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, showing a closer view of the Downtown Tammany Club.
March 31, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

721994f-a.text:
Oliver Street, east side, north from but not including Madison
Street, to and including Chatham Sduare. The view shows Public School
No. 1 on the S.E. corner of Henry Street, with the Baptist Mariner's
Temple on the N.E. corner. The Chatham Square Station of the Second
and Third Aves., Elevated Lines is shown in the background.
